<D>__{calm down.}
<A>__{they move him down the corridor. dignan's nose is bleeding. he looks terrified. applejack is sitting propped up against the wall. he's got an oxygen mask on his face and a team of paramedics and cops around him. somebody's taking his blood pressure. another one's giving him an iv.}
